{
  "id": "api/forms/FormBuilder",
  "title": "FormBuilder",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L13-L119\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L13-L119\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/FormBuilder\", \"name\": \"FormBuilder\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"formbuilder\">FormBuilder<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#formbuilder\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates an <code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a></code> from a user-specified configuration.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\">\nclass <a href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormBuilder</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#group\">group(controlsConfig: {...}, extra: {...}): FormGroup</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#control\">control(formState: any, validator?: ValidatorFn | ValidatorFn[] | null, asyncValidator?: AsyncValidatorFn | AsyncValidatorFn[] | null): FormControl</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#array\">array(controlsConfig: any[], validator?: ValidatorFn | ValidatorFn[] | null, asyncValidator?: AsyncValidatorFn | AsyncValidatorFn[] | null): FormArray</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"/guide/reactive-forms\">Reactive Forms Guide</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormBuilder</a></code> provides syntactic sugar that shortens creating instances of a <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code>,\n<code><a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a></code>, or <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormArray\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormArray</a></code>. It reduces the amount of boilerplate needed to build complex\nforms.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"group\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"group\">\n        group()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#group\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L27-L44\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L27-L44\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Construct a new <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a></code> instance.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><a href=\"api/animations/group\" class=\"code-anchor\">group</a>(controlsConfig: {\n    [key: string]: any;\n}, extra: {\n    [key: string]: any;\n} | null = null): <a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a></code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>controlsConfig</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">A collection of child controls. The key for each child is the name\nunder which it is registered.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>extra</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">An object of configuration options for the <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a></code>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>validator</code>: A synchronous validator function, or an array of validator functions</li>\n<li><code>asyncValidator</code>: A single async validator or array of async validator functions\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"\">      可选. 默认值是 <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"control\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"control\">\n        control()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#control\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L45-L73\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L45-L73\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Construct a new <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code> instance.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">control(formState: any, validator?: <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a> | <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a>[] | null, asyncValidator?: <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a> | <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a>[] | null): <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数-1\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>formState</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Initializes the control with an initial value,\nor an object that defines the initial value and disabled state.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>validator</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">A synchronous validator function, or an array of synchronous validator\nfunctions.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">      可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>asyncValidator</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">A single async validator or array of async validator functions</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">      可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值-1\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"initialize-a-control-as-disabled\">Initialize a control as disabled<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#initialize-a-control-as-disabled\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example returns a control with an initial value in a disabled state.</p>\n<code-example path=\"forms/ts/formBuilder/form_builder_example.ts\" linenums=\"false\" region=\"disabled-control\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Inject\" class=\"code-anchor\">Inject</a>} from '@angular/core';\nimport {<a href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormBuilder</a>, <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>, <a href=\"api/forms/FormGroup\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormGroup</a>, <a href=\"api/forms/Validators\" class=\"code-anchor\">Validators</a>} from '@angular/forms';\n/* . . . */\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app-disabled-form-control',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `\n    &#x3C;input [formControl]=\"control\" placeholder=\"First\">\n  `\n})\nexport class DisabledFormControlComponent {\n  control: <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>;\n\n  constructor(private fb: <a href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormBuilder</a>) {\n    this.control = fb.control({value: 'my val', disabled: true});\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"array\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"array\">\n        array()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#array\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L74-L92\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L74-L92\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Construct a new <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormArray\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormArray</a></code> instance.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">array(controlsConfig: any[], validator?: <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a> | <a href=\"api/forms/ValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidatorFn</a>[] | null, asyncValidator?: <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a> | <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\" class=\"code-anchor\">AsyncValidatorFn</a>[] | null): <a href=\"api/forms/FormArray\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormArray</a></code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数-2\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>controlsConfig</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">An array of child controls. The key for each child control is its index\nin the array.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>validator</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">A synchronous validator function, or an array of synchronous validator\nfunctions.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">      可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>asyncValidator</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">A single async validator or array of async validator functions</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">      可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值-2\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/forms/FormArray\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormArray</a></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"annotations\">\n  <h2 id=\"annotations\">注解<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormBuilder#annotations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a>()</code-example>\n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/reactive-forms\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - /guide/reactive-forms\n - api/animations/group\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/Inject\n - api/core/Injectable\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/AbstractControl\n - api/forms/AsyncValidatorFn\n - api/forms/FormArray\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#annotations\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#array\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#control\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#description\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#formbuilder\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#group\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#initialize-a-control-as-disabled\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#see-also\n - api/forms/FormBuilder#方法\n - api/forms/FormControl\n - api/forms/FormGroup\n - api/forms/ValidatorFn\n - api/forms/Validators\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L13-L119\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L27-L44\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L45-L73\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L74-L92\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L13-L119\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L27-L44\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L45-L73\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/forms/src/form_builder.ts#L74-L92\n-->"
